一、SWT ：拼接小作文

	注意事项：
	1. 每场考试1道题， 每篇不能超过70个字
	2. 一整句话不能有句号， 全部是 （，） 逗号分割
	3. 常用连词即可，because，so，and, which 或者选取原文中的句子

	最后一定 一定 一定！！！ 检查
	 全文第一句第一个词首字母大写；单词拼写；逗句号；前后空格是否正确；字数。

二、WE 大作文

	方法技巧：
	1. 从原题目中摘抄关键词和信息
	2. 如果对词汇有信心，在保证正确拼写的情况下，可以适当拓展关键词
	例如20240131那次考试，话题是climate change，作为拓展可以使用global warming关键词
	3. 注意关键词的单复数，尽量使用题目中的原词形式，注意 the；a；+s 等形式的使用 
	4. 模版文章如下：

	Nowadays, many headlines hit the newspaper on the topic of （television题目关键词). 
	This issue sparked a huge debate on （whether 基于题目改写一个whether语句）. 
	From my own point of view, I believe that （television serves many useful functions来源于题目）.


	On the one hand, there are numerous solid reasons why （television serves many useful functions）. 
	Although potentially negative impacts of （television） should be taken into account, 
	I still reckon that （television） has(这里注意前方主语单复数是用have还是has) in many ways enriched people's lives. For instance, a well-known American psychologist once said that television can make our lives more interesting.


	On the other hand, those who argue against the use of （television） hold a different opinion. 
	In the first place, it can be claimed that （television serves many useful functions）. 
	In the second place, as far as schools are concerned, the ultimate aim of schools is to shape young people into responsible people in the future. 
	As a result, local governments and international organizations should make a joint effort to reach a consensus to make sure this situation will develop in the right direction.


	In a nutshell, while there are many solid reasons on both sides, I still firmly believe that （television serves many useful functions）.


三、最后一定 一定 一定！！！ 检查
 全文第一句第一个词首字母大写；单词拼写；逗句号；前后空格是否正确；字数。
